question_title: Distinction between instance methods and static methods

question_content.description:
### Problem10
Which choice (only one) invoke static methods?

**Choices:**

a. s.startsWith("Hello")  

b. Math.sqrt(2.0)  

c. object name (or object reference)   

d. class name  

e. parameters reference to invoking object and   argument(s)   

f. argument(s)  

g. manipulate object’s value   

h. compute return value
question_content.author: Yantao Mei
choices: e. parameters reference to invoking object and   argument(s)
